===[[Min Nan]]===
[[wikipedia:POJ|POJ]]: só•-í

===Adverb===
'''[[所]][[以]]'''

# therefore; so; consequently.
#:''[[明天]][[要]][[考试]][[了]]，'''所以'''[[我]][[今天]][[只]][[能]][[留]][[在]][[家里]][[复习]][[功课]]'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#:''[[明天]][[要]][[考試]][[了]]，'''所以'''[[我]][[今天]][[只]][[能]][[留]][[在]][[家裡]][[複習]][[功課]]'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#:''I have a test tomorow, '''therefore''' I have to stay at home today and review my homework.''
# Used in the first part of a sentence to indicate a reason that will be explained in the second part of the sentence.
#:''[[我]]'''所以'''[[要]][[反对]][[这个]][[计划]]，[[是]][[因为]][[我]][[觉得]][[其中]][[有]][[不少]][[疏漏]]'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#:''[[我]]'''所以'''[[要]][[反對]][[這個]][[計畫]]，[[是]][[因為]][[我]][[覺得]][[其中]][[有]][[不少]][[疏漏]]'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#:''My '''reason''' for opposing this plan, is because I feel that there are quite a few holes in it.''

